    <label for="select">Select</label>
    <select id="select">
    <option>Option One</option>
    <option>Option Two</option>
    <option>Option Three</option>
    </select>
    <label for="textarea">Textarea</label>
    <textarea id="textarea" rows="5" cols="30" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
</form>
<h2>Images</h2>
<p>Images aren't responsive by default. However, there is a helpful <code>responsive-img</code> class to resize to 100% the width of its parent.</p>
